snippet.title: NES Longplay [273] The Lone Ranger
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by JagOfTroy

Based off the fictional character with the same name, this was another well made game by ULTRA/Konami.
It contains a few different perspectives for gameplay that are all quite entertaining with a fitting difficulty to keep it challenging but not forcing one to want to pull their hair out. -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
